\\\"tools_and_frameworks\\\": []\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nNo downstream objectives available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nBuild a recruiter communication generator to produce interview invitations and follow-up emails using templates and candidate/job data.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"interview_invitation_email\\\": {\\n    \\\"subject\\\": \\\"Interview Invitation: Software Engineer at [Company Name]\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Dear John Doe,\\\\n\\\\nWe are pleased to invite you to interview for the Software Engineer position at [Company Name]. Your resume and experience align well with the requirements of the role.\\\\n\\\\nThe interview is scheduled for [Date] at [Time] via [Platform - e.g., Zoom, Google Meet]. Please use the following link to join the meeting: [Meeting Link]\\\\n\\\\nThe interview will last approximately [Duration] and will be conducted by [Interviewer Name(s)]. We will be discussing your technical skills, experience, and how you might contribute to our team.\\\\n\\\\nPlease confirm your availability by replying to this email.\\\\n\\\\nWe look forward to speaking with you.\\\\n\\\\nSincerely,\\\\n[Your Name]\\\\n[Your Title]\\\\n[Company Name]\\\\n[Contact Information]\\\",\\n    \\\"placeholders\\\": {\\n      \\\"Company Name\\\": \\\"[Company Name - e.g., Tech Solutions Inc.]\\\",\\n      \\\"Date\\\": \\\"[Date - e.g., October 26, 2023]\\\",\\n      \\\"Time\\\": \\\"[Time - e.g., 10:00 AM PST]\\\",\\n      \\\"Platform\\\": \\\"[Platform - e.g., Zoom, Google Meet]\\\",\\n      \\\"Meeting Link\\\": \\\"[Meeting Link]\\\",\\n      \\\"Duration\\\": \\\"[Duration - e.g., 60 minutes]\\\",\\n      \\\"Interviewer Name(s)\\\": \\\"[Interviewer Name(s) - e.g., Jane Smith and David Lee]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Name\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Name]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Title\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Title]\\\",\\n      \\\"Contact Information\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Contact Information - e.g., email and phone number]\\\"\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\\"interview_follow_up_email\\\": {\\n    \\\"subject\\\": \\\"Following Up: Software Engineer Interview\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Dear John Doe,\\\\n\\\\nThank you for taking the time to interview for the Software Engineer position at [Company Name] on [Date]. We appreciate you sharing your experience and insights with us.\\\\n\\\\n[Option A: Positive Follow-up] The team was very impressed with your background and skills. We are currently in the process of considering all candidates and will be in touch within [Timeframe] with an update on the next steps.\\\\n\\\\n[Option B: Request for Additional Information] To assist us in our evaluation, we would appreciate it if you could provide [Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details] by [Date].\\\\n\\\\n[Option C: Negative Follow-up (Rejection)] After careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications and experience more closely align with the requirements of this role. We appreciate your interest in [Company Name] and encourage you to apply for other suitable positions in the future.\\\\n\\\\nThank you again for your time.\\\\n\\\\nSincerely,\\\\n[Your Name]\\\\n[Your Title]\\\\n[Company Name]\\\\n[Contact Information]\\\",\\n    \\\"placeholders\\\": {\\n      \\\"Company Name\\\": \\\"[Company Name - e.g., Tech Solutions Inc.]\\\",\\n      \\\"Date\\\": \\\"[Date - e.g., October 26, 2023]\\\",\\n      \\\"Timeframe\\\": \\\"[Timeframe - e.g., one week]\\\",\\n      \\\"Specific Information Requested\\\": \\\"[Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Name\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Name]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Title\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Title]\\\",\\n      \\\"Contact Information\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Contact Information - e.g., email and phone number]\\\"\\n    },\\n  