{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 17:24:38,266", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_validation_result", "line": 185, "message": "{\"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T17:24:38.266381\", \"task_id\": \"unknown\", \"task_objective\": \"Build a recruiter communication generator to produce interview invitations and follow-up emails using templates and candidate/job data.\", \"result\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"interview_invitation_email\\\": {\\n    \\\"subject\\\": \\\"Interview Invitation: Software Engineer at [Company Name]\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Dear John Doe,\\\\n\\\\nWe are pleased to invite you to interview for the Software Engineer position at [Company Name]. Your resume and experience align well with the requirements of the role.\\\\n\\\\nThe interview is scheduled for [Date] at [Time] via [Platform - e.g., Zoom, Google Meet]. Please use the following link to join the meeting: [Meeting Link]\\\\n\\\\nThe interview will...\", \"validation_type\": \"text\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"feedback\": \"here are some feedbacks:\\n1. The templates hard-code “John Doe” and “Software Engineer” instead of using placeholders for candidate name and job title.\\n2. The subject lines should include a `[Job Title]` placeholder rather than a fixed title.\\n3. Add `[Candidate Name]` and `[Job Title]` to the placeholders sections.\\n4. Ensure consistency: use placeholders in both subject and body.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"interview_invitation_email\\\": {\\n    \\\"subject\\\": \\\"Interview Invitation: [Job Title] at [Company Name]\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Dear [Candidate Name],\\\\n\\\\nWe are pleased to invite you to interview for the [Job Title] position at [Company Name]. Your resume and experience align well with the requirements of the role.\\\\n\\\\nThe interview is scheduled for [Date] at [Time] via [Platform - e.g., Zoom, Google Meet]. Please use the following link to join the meeting: [Meeting Link]\\\\n\\\\nThe interview will last approximately [Duration] and will be conducted by [Interviewer Name(s)]. We will be discussing your technical skills, experience, and how you might contribute to our team.\\\\n\\\\nPlease confirm your availability by replying to this email.\\\\n\\\\nWe look forward to speaking with you.\\\\n\\\\nSincerely,\\\\n[Your Name]\\\\n[Your Title]\\\\n[Company Name]\\\\n[Contact Information]\\\",\\n    \\\"placeholders\\\": {\\n      \\\"Candidate Name\\\": \\\"[Candidate Name - e.g., John Doe]\\\",\\n      \\\"Job Title\\\": \\\"[Job Title - e.g., Software Engineer]\\\",\\n      \\\"Company Name\\\": \\\"[Company Name - e.g., Tech Solutions Inc.]\\\",\\n      \\\"Date\\\": \\\"[Date - e.g., October 26, 2023]\\\",\\n      \\\"Time\\\": \\\"[Time - e.g., 10:00 AM PST]\\\",\\n      \\\"Platform\\\": \\\"[Platform - e.g., Zoom, Google Meet]\\\",\\n      \\\"Meeting Link\\\": \\\"[Meeting Link]\\\",\\n      \\\"Duration\\\": \\\"[Duration - e.g., 60 minutes]\\\",\\n      \\\"Interviewer Name(s)\\\": \\\"[Interviewer Name(s) - e.g., Jane Smith and David Lee]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Name\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Name]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Title\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Title]\\\",\\n      \\\"Contact Information\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Contact Information - e.g., email and phone number]\\\"\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\\"interview_follow_up_email\\\": {\\n    \\\"subject\\\": \\\"Following Up: [Job Title] Interview\\\",\\n    \\\"body\\\": \\\"Dear [Candidate Name],\\\\n\\\\nThank you for taking the time to interview for the [Job Title] position at [Company Name] on [Date]. We appreciate you sharing your experience and insights with us.\\\\n\\\\n[Option A: Positive Follow-up]\\\\nThe team was very impressed with your background and skills. We are currently in the process of considering all candidates and will be in touch within [Timeframe] with an update on the next steps.\\\\n\\\\n[Option B: Request for Additional Information]\\\\nTo assist us in our evaluation, we would appreciate it if you could provide [Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details] by [Date].\\\\n\\\\n[Option C: Negative Follow-up (Rejection)]\\\\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications and experience more closely align with the requirements of this role. We appreciate your interest in [Company Name] and encourage you to apply for other suitable positions in the future.\\\\n\\\\nThank you again for your time.\\\\n\\\\nSincerely,\\\\n[Your Name]\\\\n[Your Title]\\\\n[Company Name]\\\\n[Contact Information]\\\",\\n    \\\"placeholders\\\": {\\n      \\\"Candidate Name\\\": \\\"[Candidate Name - e.g., John Doe]\\\",\\n      \\\"Job Title\\\": \\\"[Job Title - e.g., Software Engineer]\\\",\\n      \\\"Company Name\\\": \\\"[Company Name - e.g., Tech Solutions Inc.]\\\",\\n      \\\"Date\\\": \\\"[Date - e.g., October 26, 2023]\\\",\\n      \\\"Timeframe\\\": \\\"[Timeframe - e.g., one week]\\\",\\n      \\\"Specific Information Requested\\\": \\\"[Specific Information Requested - e.g., references, code samples, project details]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Name\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Name]\\\",\\n      \\\"Your Title\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Title]\\\",\\n      \\\"Contact Information\\\": \\\"[Recruiter Contact Information - e.g., email and phone number]\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"options\\\": [\\n      \\\"Positive Follow-up\\\",\\n      \\\"Request for Additional Information\\\",\\n      \\\"Negative Follow-up (Rejection)\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"}"}
